564
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,640
Shit.

565
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:28,700
He's usually only with you.

566
00:29:29,260 --> 00:29:30,040
He's right.

567
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,760
But there's still hope.

568
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,600
